      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p>Propose a structure for compound <b>E</b>, C<sub>7</sub>H<sub>12</sub>O<sub>2</sub>, which has the following <sup>13</sup>C NMR spectral data:</p>\n<p><b>Compound E</b></p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:none\">\n<li>Broadband-decoupled <sup>13</sup>C NMR: 19.1, 28.0, 70.5, 129.0, 129.8, 165.8 <i>δ</i></li>\n<li>DEPT-90: 28.0, 129.8 <i>δ</i></li>\n<li>DEPT-135: positive peaks at 19.1, 28.0, 129.8 <i>δ;</i> negative peaks at 70.5, 129.0 <i>δ</i></li>\n</ul>",
